    dc:description "FIGURES 28A–L. Hexapopha tallitae sp. nov., SEM images. A–I male (MPEG 37103; PBI_OON 46100). J–L female (MPEG 37097; PBI_OON 44879). A–B carapace. A lateral view. B ventral view. C mouthparts, ventral view. D–E endites, lateral view (asterisk: prolateral process of P1). F–G left palp. F prolateral view. G retrolateral view. H–I embolus. H prolateral view. I retrolateral view. J epigastric region, ventral view. K internal genitalia, dorsal view. L detail of K, showing genital duct. Abbreviations: d, duct; mp, median projection; P, projection." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8244089/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8244097>
    dc:description "FIGURES 31A–L. Hexapopha platnicki sp. nov., SEM images. A–H male (MPEG 37731; PBI_OON 45513). I–L female (MPEG 37731; PBI_OON 45513). A carapace, ventral view. B endites, ventral view (asterisk: prolateral process of P1). C detail of B, showing projection P2. D abdomen, lateral view. E–F left palp. E prolateral view. F retrolateral view. G–H embolus. G prolateral view. H retrolateral view. I carapace, ventrolateral view. J epigastric region, ventral view. K internal genitalia, dorsal view. L detail of K, showing T-shaped anterior genitalic process.Abbreviations: as, anterior sclerite; d, duct; mp, median projection; P, projection." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8244097/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8244181>
    dc:description "FIGURES 60A–L. Hexapopha numerosa sp. nov., SEM images. A–I male (MPEG 37036; PBI_OON 46329). J–L female (MPEG 15316; PBI_OON 45438). A habitus, lateral view. B carapace, ventral view. C mouthparts, ventral view. D endites, showing median projections and projection P1. E–F left palp. E prolateral view. F retrolateral view. G–I embolus. G prolateral view. H retrolateral view. I apical view. J epigastric region, ventral view. K internal genitalia, dorsal view (arrow: slit-shaped opening on posterior uterine sclerite). L detail of J, copulatory opening. Abbreviations: as, anterior sclerite; d, duct; mp, median projection; P, projection; vs, ventral surface of distal hook of posterior sclerite." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8244181/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8244187>
    dc:description "FIGURES 63A–L. Hexapopha baehrae sp. nov., SEM images. A–I male (MCN 8554; PBI_OON 46377). J–L female (MCN 8554; PBI_OON 46377). A carapace, ventral view. B mouthparts, ventral view. C endites ventral view. D chelicerae, posterior view. E sperm pore, ventral view. F–G left palp. F prolateral view. G retrolateral view. H–I embolus. H prolateral view. I retrolateral view. J epigastric region, ventral view. K internal genitalia, dorsal view. L detail of K, showing T-shaped anterior genitalic process. Abbreviations: as, anterior sclerite; mp, median projection; P, projection." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8244187/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

