    dc:description "FIGURES 65A–H. Hexapopha excavata sp. nov., female (MPEG 10971; PBI_OON 45364). A–B habitus. A dorsal view. B lateral view. C–E carapace. C dorsal view. D ventral view. E anterior view. F abdomen, ventral view. G–H epigastric region. G ventral view. H dorsal view. Scale bars: 0.1mm." ;
